Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:32.70,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:34.59,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Katsuki Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:36.49,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Russian Punk, Yurio,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:40.18,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,has come in pursuit of my coach, \NVictor, all hell's broken loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:45.33,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Hot Springs on Ice event is now being \Nheld so that Yurio and I can face off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.45,0:01:45.33,WorldChampion2,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}Hasetsu Exhibition \N{\c&H5E41B2&}Hot Springs {\c&H9C7233&}on Ice \NPresented by {\c&H5E41B2&}Victor Nikiforov
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:49.58,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If Yurio wins, Victor will go back \Nto Russia and be Yurio's coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:53.96,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, Victor will stay in \NJapan and be my coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:57.97,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm gonna give it all the eros I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:02.97,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Third Skate \N{\fs20}I Am Eros, and Eros Is Me?! \NFace-Off! Hot Springs on Ice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I Am Eros, and Eros Is Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:02.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Face-off! Hot Springs on Ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:08.48,Default - italics,V,0000,0000,0000,,First, Yurio's "On Love: Agape."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:21.57,Default - italics,V,0000,0000,0000,,Agape... Unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:27.64,Default - italics,V,0000,0000,0000,,God's infinite love is \Nself-sacrificing and uncalculating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:34.25,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, this is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:37.26,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Victor can pull it off,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.26,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I wonder how Yurio will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:46.89,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of like that. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:48.89,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I pretty much got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:49.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.40,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.65,Default,Yurio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who's that chick?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.65,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's one of the staff here, Yuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:00.38,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for interrupting your practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:02.68,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,It was so wonderful, I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.79,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Yuri. You're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:07.58,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:08.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:13.42,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Choreography that Victor did for me alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:17.63,Default - italics,V,0000,0000,0000,,"On Love: Eros."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.43,SFX,Sign 0322,0000,0000,0000,,Spurt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:26.84,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eros... Sexual love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:29.31,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure followed by pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.17,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One just drowns in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.85,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn, he's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.45,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What the... Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:36.90,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough to make even me, \Na man, pregnant! Such eros!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.36,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.67,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Can I skate this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:44.24,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.90,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:48.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:50.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It was very "eros"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:51.36,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:54.12,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,So, about the program composition... \NWhich quads can you land?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:56.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The toe loop, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I can land the Salchow in practice, \Nbut never in competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:03.47,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I think I can do it if I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.51,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you can practice the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.89,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach Yurio first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.89,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I won't teach you anything \Nyou can't do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:16.15,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have you messed \Nup during a competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:19.53,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,You have the skill to win.\NWhy can't you make it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's probably because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I lack confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:28.87,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Right. My job is to make you \Nfeel confident in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:37.64,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,No one in the whole wide world \Nknows your true eros, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:40.84,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,It may be an alluring side of you \Nthat you yourself are unaware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:44.34,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Can you show me what it is soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:47.09,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Victor! Aren't you teaching me first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.55,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:49.60,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,So, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:54.48,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Think long and hard about \Nwhat eros is to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:57.73,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What eros is to me? What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.98,WorldChampion2,Sign 0459,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hot Springs on Ice \NYuri vs. Yurio \NHasetsu Exhibition!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:02.99,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew we'd get a lineup like this in Hasetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.16,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of people will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.74,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Well, either way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.87,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri's back! Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.99,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:12.44,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.52,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,You had to do basic training for half \Na day because you didn't get "eros"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:16.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.30,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,You should have just made something up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:21.75,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Victor hasn't thought \Nmuch about it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:25.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Victor's a genius, so he can get away with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:31.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I could see a story in the program, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A playboy comes to a certain town
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and bewitches the women left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:41.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He decides to pursue the most \Nbeautiful woman in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:42.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but she isn't swayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:45.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as they play the game of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:48.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,she finds it difficult to make the right choices
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:50.31,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and ends up falling for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:54.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Then he casts her aside, \Nas though he's tired of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,and goes off to the next town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:59.29,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,"Wow! So hot! Take me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:02.71,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't really sound like you, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:03.55,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:07.42,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I bet people will say they'd prefer \Nto see Victor skate the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:11.05,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,But you looked pretty sexy in the video \Nwhen you copied his program.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't copy him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never surpass him by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:19.37,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you seriously think you can \Nbe better than him someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:19.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:21.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um, no, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.95,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, how can someone as\Ninexperienced in dating as you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.26,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,beat the hottest bachelor in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:28.95,SFX,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Ha ha ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.02,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:34.20,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, something isn't right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.62,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it like you showed me, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.58,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,The way you currently are,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.54,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,your greed is too obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:45.04,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sense of agape, unconditional \Nlove, in your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:47.27,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to have confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:49.84,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,but this program isn't where \Nyou should show it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:50.99,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:54.35,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's skated with \Ncomplete confidence this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:57.35,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what's agape to you, then, Victor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.60,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,It's a feeling, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.64,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,so I could never explain it in words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:04.11,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Do you bother thinking about \Nthat when you skate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.86,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,You're funny, Yurio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.61,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe we need a temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:10.62,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,A temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.62,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.13,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:24.96,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an adult male of twenty-three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.26,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I could totally show mature \Nsexiness if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.08,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:33.51,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Take a photo of me in the bath \Nso I can post it online.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:38.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we don't let people \Ntake photos in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:39.39,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.69,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.52,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,From a physical standpoint, \NI'm not even close to eros.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.18,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Eros, eros...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:52.04,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's what causes you to lose the \Nability to make normal decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:57.28,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,For me, what causes me to \Nlose that ability is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.74,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:00.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Pork cutlet bowls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:01.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's what eros is to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:04.67,Title,Sign 0803,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Silence...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:08.17,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.92,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.76,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice and unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.04,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:15.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:19.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They totally think my ideas \Nare way too immature!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.67,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.88,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Try to imagine entangling more of the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.24,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Think of the pork cutlet bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:30.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:31.63,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Yurio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:43.87,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.58,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me if I'm not up to par!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.76,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Your free leg's sloppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.49,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.32,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Put your back into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:19.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:25.08,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.83,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe a waterfall would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.83,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,A waterfall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:32.62,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.89,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Why me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:35.88,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:36.34,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.16,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about agape?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.67,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Forget all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:44.47,Default - flashback,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,Yuratchka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:47.00,Default - flashback,Gramps,0000,0000,0000,,You were the best of the bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.76,Default - flashback,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, can you come to \Npractice again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:52.36,Default - flashback,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I can skate even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:55.36,Default - flashback,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, even if Mom's not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yurio?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:01.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yurio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.75,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.27,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.15,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he suddenly look so vulnerable?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:20.46,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... Where's Victor, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:22.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He went to eat at Nagahama Ramen, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.09,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:24.17,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,We're going there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:25.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:27.89,Ramen,Sign 1025,0000,0000,0000,,Nagahama Ramen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.89,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Vkusno!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:30.40,sign_31018_532_Hasetsu_Exhibiti,Sign 1029,0000,0000,0000,,Hasetsu Exhibition \N"Hot Springs On Ice" in {\c&H203195&}1 {\c&H576362&}Day
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Victor still isn't here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:35.15,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,They said he was drinking until dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:35.90,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.32,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yurio...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.34,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:40.94,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:43.33,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me how to land a quad Salchow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:44.54,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:51.39,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:54.12,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Pork Cutlet Bowl. \NWatch me do it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.34,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.46,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.88,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,What were you practicing just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:01.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna check my choreography.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.31,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Agape...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:11.83,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.94,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,To me, that means Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.96,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Yurio found his agape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.07,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's ready for the next stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.31,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Next stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:28.33,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I have a next stage, once \NI perform the eros of the pork cutlet bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:31.98,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't find it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:38.34,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I still lack what would serve as \Nthe backbone this program needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.68,Yutopia,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasetsu Hot Springs \NYu-topia Katsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.89,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you do for a costume tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.65,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I totally forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.39,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring anything, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.98,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,That's taken care of!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:52.19,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I had them send all the costumes I've ever \Nworn in competition from Russia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:53.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.13,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of stupid-looking ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:58.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you wore this one at the \NGrand Prix Final last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:00.15,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't pick anything flashier than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This is from the Junior World Championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:03.55,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.31,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I had long hair at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:08.10,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,so my costume suggested both \Nmale and female genders at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.31,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I choose this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.34,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:19.38,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:22.59,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,You want to practice in my \Nstudio this late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:27.18,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Minako-sensei, I need you \Nto teach me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:40.23,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,We're here at Ice Castle Hasetsu, venue of \Nthe Hasetsu Exhibition: Hot Springs on Ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.61,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Right off the bat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:45.24,TV,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasetsu Exhibition: Hot Springs on Ice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:45.24,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,we have skaters Katsuki Yuri and Yuri Plisetsky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:48.58,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Both your new short programs were \Nchoreographed by Victor Nikiforov.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:50.89,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be presenting them today in competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.75,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us how you feel going into the event!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:57.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it'd be great if you'd try \Nthe hot springs afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:13:13.89,TV,Sign 1253,0000,0000,0000,,Hasetsu Exhibition: Hot Springs on Ice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:59.07,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We're not asking you to promote tourism!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.28,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Promote yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:02.34,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need two Yuris. I'll crush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.48,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's it! Thanks for giving \Nus what we wanted to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:05.89,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Spasibo, spasibo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:08.11,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Last but not least, let's hear \Nfrom Victor Nikiforov,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:10.31,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,who's switched to coaching out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:13.89,Phone,Sign 1311,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\c&H7267A8&}Hasetsu {\c&H503B38&}Tourism Ambassador
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:11.09,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:13.88,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Hasetsu is a great place. \N Come and visit at least once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:16.22,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:19.27,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! It makes today's \Nface-off look cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:22.40,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be ready to evaluate our battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grant the wish of whichever \None of us wins, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.18,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:27.85,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.53,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:37.04,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you for coming to the Hasetsu \NExhibition: Hot Springs on Ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.01,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:37.04,Default,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been since \Nso many people were in this rink?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.71,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8} presented by Victor Nikiforov.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:46.72,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurio-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.34,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:50.35,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:58.94,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's the see-through costume of legend \Nfrom Victor's junior days!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.75,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd see it in \Nperson! It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:03.69,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,You're gushing all kinds of fluids again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.94,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You look really good in it! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.61,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.36,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.99,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:15.25,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Now, a champion with wins in the Junior Grand \NPrix Final and Junior World Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.21,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Hoping for a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.34,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,brilliant senior division debut, with programs \Nchoreographed by Victor Nikiforov,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:22.42,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri Plisetsky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Davai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:28.44,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, davai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:30.11,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,Davai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:31.39,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, davai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:37.11,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He will be skating to "On Love: Agape."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:53.00,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His first jump is a triple axel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.58,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:06.50,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's drawn into Yurio's agape performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:10.84,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell it's completely different \Nfrom what I saw in practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.85,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,That's when Yurio's performance changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:22.55,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,No one can look away from this \Nbeautiful, ever-evolving monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:30.84,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,We're approaching the quadruples he was \Nprohibited from performing in competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.11,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention they're in the \Nsecond half of his program.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:37.22,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple Salchow, \Nfollowed by a triple toe loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:39.22,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He unveiled the quad with a flourish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:46.41,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes his final jump, \Na quadruple toe loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.70,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.46,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,What an astonishing fifteen-year-old!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:53.07,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He nailed all of his jumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.14,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.86,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too busy trying to skate the program
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.73,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,to really think about agape at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.86,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,The last element is his signature move, \Nthe combination spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:12.86,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.41,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Just end already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.48,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! A masterful performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.80,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot to look forward \Nto this coming season!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.21,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm better than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:33.22,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yurio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:36.22,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,That was the best performance \NI've seen from you so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:37.86,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, greet the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:42.50,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri Plisetsky, who's enthralled the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:45.63,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.46,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He'll definitely rank among the \Ntop senior division skaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.22,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.22,0:16:53.02,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose, Victor will go back to Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:54.53,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:55.90,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:57.29,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:58.27,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I want to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.10,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:01.29,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:08.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:11.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become a super\Ntasty pork cutlet bowl,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:13.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so please watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:18.49,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.47,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I love pork cutlet bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:24.83,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,We're pleased to introduce a skater \Nwho represents Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.98,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,a late bloomer who's become a rising star,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.96,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuki Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.37,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good luck, Yuri-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:35.08,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He will skate to "On Love: Eros."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:34.56,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:37.53,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good luck, Katsuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:38.47,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He's been having difficulty expressing "eros,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:41.39,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,but he said he'll think of how he'd \Nlove to eat his favorite dish,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.49,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,the pork cutlet bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:44.75,Default - italics,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,I pulled an all-nighter to help him practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:47.77,Default - italics,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,and he's no ordinary pork cutlet bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:54.01,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I dancing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:55.97,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:36.17,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,What a seductive step sequence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:38.72,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe he's\Nimagining a pork cutlet bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:39.68,Default - italics,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:43.18,Default - italics,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,You're known for your step sequences and spins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:46.18,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to teach me how \Nto move in feminine ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.49,Default - flashback,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:49.34,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to be the playboy isn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:52.69,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be the most beautiful woman \Nin town, who seduces the playboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.27,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I won't drastically change any moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:59.70,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I think this is a lot closer to how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:03.03,Default - italics,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I wasn't sure what he \Nwas being all serious about,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:06.27,Default - italics,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,but his performance has \Nintegrated his emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.23,Default - italics,Minako,0000,0000,0000,,It's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:13.63,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we have a spread eagle into a triple axel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.76,Default - italics,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this program is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:20.02,Default - italics,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Scheduling all the jumps in the second \Nhalf just because he has stamina
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:20.92,Default - italics,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,is pretty spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:25.38,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! He stepped out of \Nhis quadruple Salchow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:28.00,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He managed to stay on his feet \Nby putting his hand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.14,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,About what you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.73,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:34.32,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A mistake like this isn't enough \Nto make me lose my charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:38.36,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm better than any other woman out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.53,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You ask why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:42.41,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple toe loop, \Nfollowed by a triple toe loop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.62,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.13,Default - italics,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,A quad-triple combination \Nat the very end? Is he insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:49.53,Default - italics,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,He nailed it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:10.43,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:11.94,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:12.40,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, it's not "welcome back."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:14.92,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,That was a Yuri you've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.44,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,No one could look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:19.94,Default,Nishi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to this season now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.44,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.34,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,That was the tastiest pork \Ncutlet bowl I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:26.42,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:31.20,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,But can I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:32.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:35.12,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,What was with your triple axel \Nout of the spread eagle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:36.30,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,That was the worst attempt so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.42,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I know you had Yurio teach you the quad \NSalchow in secret, but what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.63,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.47,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurio-kun, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:46.43,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're going back without even \Nhearing the results?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:48.81,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I already know the results.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.06,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,That performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:55.12,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep going under Yakov.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.02,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:57.19,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Dasvidaniya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:20:58.94,Default,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:00.89,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.44,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who'll win at \Nthe Grand Prix Final!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.82,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:12.70,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuki Yuri has won the \NHot Springs on Ice event.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.38,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,A word, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:17.71,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:26.03,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to try and win the next \NGrand Prix Final with Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:28.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your continued support!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:36.14,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The battle for my very last \Nfigure skating season has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:40.02,TBC,Sign 2138,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:14.24,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd even be happy to see me naked on ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:16.74,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, I would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:18.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:19.91,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Fourth Skate:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:21.93,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Like Yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:26.01,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Fourth Skate \N{\fs20}Like Yourself... \NAnd Complete the Free Program!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:24.04,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,And Complete the Free Program!!
